  "text": "Creativity is (despite all the visual noise and advertising of the airport billboards claiming otherwise,) rather silent, still, slow -and small in size. It is a passing moment, a blink of the eye. It is a relational movement. One has prepared oneself to be unprepared. One has allowed oneself to be surprised, in the company of others [CITATION_1] .",
